Package: chuck.a.luck.simulator
Title: Statistical Simulator for the Game 'Chuck-a-Luck'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        "Christian Joseph", "Bunyi",
        email = "cj.bunyi.dev@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-6703-0144")
    )
Description: Simulates the 'Chuck-a-Luck' dice game to empirically demonstrate
    frequentist statistics concepts, specifically the Law of Large Numbers.
    The 'shiny' application provides visualizations of convergence and calculates
    confidence intervals for matching dice outcomes.
